item.description: Biography I am a fresh graduate from the department of Computer Science and Engineering, IIT Kanpur who is currently working as a software developer in VISA, Bengaluru. During my time as an undergraduate, I worked on various projects in the fields of Machine Learning, Cyber Security and Computer Systems. Along with this, I have spent a summer as an intern at VISA. Some other startups which I have worked before are, namely Sharechat and Elanic.
